text: == Events == * The Chavda Kingdom is overthrown in Gujarat, India. * October 30 – Pope Marinus II succeeds Pope Stephen VIII as the 128th pope. == Births == * Pampa, Kannada poet in India * Genshin, Tendai scholar == Deaths == * King Idwal Foel of Gwynedd * December 17 – William I of Normandy * Gaozu of Later Jin, founder of the Later Jin Dynasty in China * Liu Yan of the Southern Han Kingdom
